rows.label: tlk45500421_01_msg0001
rows.name: And who might you be, hmm?

rows.label: tlk45500421_01_msg0002
rows.name:
From the looks of you... You must be
here to ask my advice, I suppose?

rows.label: tlk45500421_01_msg0003
rows.name:
I see, I see... Must've gotten
the wrong end of the stick.

rows.label: tlk45500421_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Drivers often come to me asking
for advice on their work, you know.

rows.label: tlk45500421_01_msg0005
rows.name:
I'm retired now - age does take its
toll - but I had quite the career as
a Driver myself, you see.

rows.label: tlk45500421_01_msg0006
rows.name:
Though at this point, I'm no different
from any other old man living out my
remaining days in peace.
